{"tid":894973,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人試過鬼剃頭","createTime":"2018-11-08T19:58:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-09T11:07:04.000Z","uid":172778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"8ebf797a20b62fb6918e3296101471dc5f97d2d6","tid":894973,"uid":172778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T19:58:09.000Z","msg":"突然發現個頭禿左一個大約一個5蚊銀大細嘅圓型<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔知係咪之前返工壓力大<br />\n有無人試過<br />\n知唔知有無咩藥膏擦下會好D<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雖然長頭髮唔係好覺眼，但好驚會甩哂D頭髮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"933f1e2f10603938ddb6d4dd07ba82e423bdddb9","tid":894973,"uid":116053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T20:06:25.000Z","msg":"我試過<br />\n邊個位?"},{"pid":"11c215031e9afc1345e6b2d5756dbf39148a5092","tid":894973,"uid":16096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T20:22:26.000Z","msg":"有 我成日都有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n要噴野 同唔好成日俾大壓力自己"},{"pid":"624bad9fd67e8dcf0fde7afd2f7a7922ae2b710d","tid":894973,"uid":185022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T20:35:17.000Z","msg":"我試過,要睇中醫"},{"pid":"d37a28fae3b37a275aaee2f542a2918f5168dbc4","tid":894973,"uid":185022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T20:39:27.000Z","msg":"補一補充,係我小六嘅事,好嚴重,成個頭甩到一塊塊咁,最少四大撻禿左。<br />\n最後老師介紹我去仁濟醫院中醫部睇,用左大半年醫返。<br />\n嗰時中醫話係免疫失調,中醫角度好似叫油風病(詳細唔記得,成十年前嘅事"},{"pid":"93783803edda25bd2cec5ba574c7eb58b7a10eba","tid":894973,"uid":126649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T20:46:22.000Z","msg":"試過 打咗類固醇落頭皮 幾個月就好返"},{"pid":"2c932a39f078ae71fcab650b6aeae26a004c790d","tid":894973,"uid":194876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T11:07:04.000Z","msg":"我細佬甩到雞蛋咁大<br />\n之後自動好番"}]}